content.description:
Squat start with hands matched on a sidepull (same start as

Minnesota Nice

). From there, traverse right through an undercling, bump through a right hand edge to a jug sidepull, gain the lip, and finish up the edges on the slab (same finish as

Seven Minute Itch

).

The difficulty can be doubled by eliminating the sidepull jug before the slab section. It uses a right hand crimp and a difficult undercling. It's an enjoyable sequence.
